{ struct input_event #linux-input_event

  The *event structure*.

  Depending on the value of some values, the struct might have the following members:
code {
struct input_event {

  struct timeval time;

  __u16 type;
  __u16 code;
  __s32 value;
}
code }

  Compare with → Linux/kernel/source/include/linux/input_h#linux-input_value[`struct input_value`] found in `→ Linux/kernel/source/include/linux/input_h`.

  See also the → development/languages/Python/libraries/evdev#py-evdev-InputEvent[`events.InputEvent`] class found in the → development/languages/Python/libraries/evdev[Python library `evdev`].

}

